<item>
            <title>[OPENJPA-1148] Build failures with 64bit Sun JDK6 on Linux due to PermGen space</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OPENJPA-1148</link>
                <project id="12310351" key="OPENJPA">OpenJPA</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We&apos;re seeing builds fail with OOM PermGen space when using 64bit Sun JDK6 (but not IBM SDK 6) on Linux (but not MacOSX.)&lt;br/&gt;
This will involve 2 parts:&lt;br/&gt;
1) updating the test.jvm.arguments and surefire.jvm.args in the pom.xml files&lt;br/&gt;
2) users and automated build servers will need to update their MAVEN_OPTS if they want to build with a 64bit JVM&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
